title: Britney Spears to end her Las Vegas residency?
text:
Other Articles Sugar, yes please! 5 reasons why it is added to foods No one thought I could carry off 'Aahalya', says Radhika Apte Oral drug to treat alcholism may be available in 5 years! Pop star Britney Spears says she is not sure if she wants to continue her Las Vegas residency although she had lots of fun performing the shows.
“I’m not really sure. I haven’t made up my mind. I really love doing the show. It’s a lot, a lot of fun but I’m kind of torn right now. I don’t really know what I want to do,” Britney Spears said.
Britney Spears’ “Piece of Me” show, which was kicked off in December 2013, has been a huge success.
If Britney Spears ends up deciding not to renew her deal, her last performances at Planet Hollywood will happen later this month until October with the final shows scheduled over New Year’s weekend.
Britney Spears, 33, is currently also busy working on her new music.
“We’re having fun right now. I’m working with some women who are amazing writers. I have ballads and, of course, dance music – fun cheeky sexy stuff.”
 19, 2015 11:22 am
